{"tid":785601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手復合？","createTime":"2018-08-19T10:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T04:02:47.000Z","uid":202357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd0441f2a2a657e97d3311c49dc6e716210f046","tid":785601,"uid":202357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過分手超過四個月，最後係可以復合？<br />\n我同男朋友一齊左五年幾，前排分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話覺得好大壓力好想休息下<br />\n佢啲朋友話比我知佢而家仲係愛我同唔捨得<br />\n佢又從來冇好決絕咁話以後冇可能一齊番<br />\n佢五年幾黎都好愛我對我好好 <br />\n會花好多時間同心機係我身上<br />\n同埋我地之間冇第三者，分手對雙方黎講都係好突然<br />\n呢段日子雖然冇乜聯絡 但都感受到佢仲係關心我<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁長既感情分手 有冇機會一齊番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906361cae43292e44137f62fad6956a3d3048d72","tid":785601,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"食咗五年同一味餸<br />\n都係時候轉下<br />\n回憶的味道間唔中回味下就夠<br />\n<br />\n復合？不了<br />\nSp大歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a747fd48585074ebc711eaeb585c982647ba0e06","tid":785601,"uid":161537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:18:01.000Z","msg":"有時女人真係好蠢<br />\n成日深信一啲分手理由唔係理由"},{"pid":"64514a7eb9f3a531fe0b0f87153d7edd5d5dee9d","tid":785601,"uid":186711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"直接問？<br />\n問咗都唔得就唔好奢望啦"},{"pid":"f4d9645eb7bef971ba6ed5c668fedc406d573e3c","tid":785601,"uid":148995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"樓主 最後成功嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近有同你90%相似嘅經歷 所以search返關於復合嘅主題搵到你舊Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094e92e207a2fbb3e19b2ab9712fb885131aeb1a","tid":785601,"uid":202357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d9645eb7bef971ba6ed5c668fedc406d573e3c","tid":785601,"uid":148995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"樓主 最後成功嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近有同你90%相似嘅經歷 所以search返關於復合嘅主題搵到你舊Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"最後對方返左黎搵我 但係差唔多一齊返既時候<br />\n佢最後識左第二個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實分得手 所有野都已經唔同哂 <br />\n就算佢返黎都只會係因為唔捨得<br />\n分手成功復合 再走到最後就係冇乜幾可做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}